txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: lethal sharp claws from cave-claws to the south of Aughaire. Deliver the items to Raith at Aughaire in the south-western reaches of Angmar.
'These can be fashioned into many weapons. Thank you.'
'The beasts that tunnel in the earth to the south have sharp claws that can be fashioned into small weapons... would you gather some for us?'
Council of the North Task: Lethal Sharp Claws
The Hillmen at Aughaire have requested a collection of lethal sharp claws to be delivered to Raith.
Deliver the lethal sharp claws to Raith at Aughaire in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver lethal sharp claws from cave-claws surrounding Aughaire to Raith, a Hillman within the settlement.
Wanted: lethal sharp claws from cave-claws to the south of Aughaire.
